<br>
What I would like to see, in games of this type is what I suggested earlier. Categorize players and design servers around them (elite to causal, to pvp, to roleplay etc.). <br>
<br>
The feeling I got from Brad's reply was that the tendency for the future is that there will be different games to cater to different player classes. What I would like to see more of is all games catering to all (or specific levels of players).<br>
<br>
To me this would allow a company to reach a broader audience as well as benefit players. It may be too late for an established game such as EQ, but it would have been nice to see elite servers for the hard core gamers, and casual types for, well, the casual types. <br>
<br>
BTW: <br>
Shadowy, Loved some of your ideas!<br>
